data.description: CHARMING 2BR/2.5BA Townhome in Epernay, a quiet, peaceful community adjacent to the lavish  green Lakeside CC and minutes away from Energy Corridor, offering the best of Houston living. Seller  is the original owner and an interior designer, which is evident in his beautifully curated furnishings  and meticulous maintenance. Open air atrium patio, just off the kitchen/breakfast room, with mature trees and beautiful water effect, inviting you to morning coffee or evening wine! Brand new upgrades includes new front door and new pavers in the front patio. Water heater and A/C unit only three years young!  Community amenities abound, with centrally located clubhouse, sparkling pool and tennis courts just a few steps away. MUST SEE!!
